96
00:11:01,831 --> 00:11:03,266
风挡过热警示
Windshield hot caution.

97
00:11:12,442 --> 00:11:13,943
机身温度升高
Surface temp rising.

98
00:11:19,449 --> 00:11:21,418
快啊，宝贝，再快一点
Come on sweetheart just a little more.

99
00:11:22,218 --> 00:11:23,253
