Just a little.

100
00:11:27,023 --> 00:11:28,058
快啊！
Come on!

101
00:11:34,597 --> 00:11:35,398
快啊！
Come on!

102
00:11:41,037 --> 00:11:42,038
10马赫！
Mach 10!

103
