Earth.

117
00:13:53,002 --> 00:13:54,404
独行侠
Maverick.

118
00:13:55,105 --> 00:13:56,940
三十多年的军旅生涯
Thirty-plus years of service.

119
00:13:57,941 --> 00:13:59,409
战功勋章
Combat medals.

120
00:13:59,542 --> 00:14:00,944
奖项无数
Citations.

121
00:14:01,544 --> 00:14:06,082
四十年来唯一击落三架敌机的人
Only man to shoot down three enemy planes
in the last 40 years.

122
00:14:06,683 --> 00:14:07,884
杰出服役勋章
"Distinguished."

123
00:14:08,017 --> 00:14:11,721
杰出服役勋章、杰出服役勋章
"Distinguished." "Distinguished."

124
00:14:13,423 --> 00:14:16,726
但你却升不了官，也不肯退役
Yet you can't get a promotion you won't retire

125
00:14:16,826 --> 00:14:19,896
尽管多次出生入死，却又死不了
and despite your best efforts you refuse to die.

126
00:14:20,397 --> 00:14:24,434
早就该成为二星少将，或是参议员
You should be at least a two-star admiral
by now if not a senator.

127
00:14:25,101 --> 00:14:26,636
但你仍留在这里
Yet here you are:

128
00:14:28,271 --> 00:14:29,372
