Captain.

129
00:14:30,473 --> 00:14:31,908
为什么？
Why is that?

130
00:14:32,609 --> 00:14:34,144
人生就是如此难解，长官
It's one of life's mysteries sir.

131
00:14:34,277 --> 00:14:37,914
这不是笑话，我在问你问题
This isn't a joke. I asked you a question.

132
00:14:39,716 --> 00:14:41,484
这是我的归属，长官
I'm where I belong sir.

133
00:14:42,085 --> 00:14:44,754
海军不这么认为
Well the navy doesn't see it that way.

134
00:14:45,822 --> 00:14:46,923
