North Island sir?

147
00:15:35,105 --> 00:15:37,674
有一通电话来得时机刚刚好
Call came in with impeccable timing

148
00:15:37,807 --> 00:15:41,344
就在我准备罚你永远禁飞之前
right as I was driving here to
ground your ass once and for all.

149
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:45,348
我很不想说，但是…
It galls me to say it but...

150
00:15:46,850 --> 00:15:50,553
只有老天爷和你的守护天使知道原因
for reasons known only to
the Almighty and your guardian angel...

151
00:15:52,555 --> 00:15:55,125
你又被召回扞卫战士学校
you've been called back to TOPGUN.

152
