-长官？
-解散，上校
-Sir?
-You are dismissed Captain.

153
00:16:07,904 --> 00:16:09,839
结局是无可避免的，独行侠
The end is inevitable Maverick.

154
00:16:10,707 --> 00:16:12,642
你这种飞官总有一天会被淘汰
Your kind is headed for extinction.

155
00:16:16,346 --> 00:16:18,014
也许吧，长官
Maybe so sir.

156
00:16:19,582 --> 00:16:21,151
但不是今天
But not today.

