to our allies in the region.

178
00:18:15,932 --> 00:18:19,969
国防部要求我们召集攻击小队
The Pentagon has tasked us with
assembling a strike team and taking it out

179
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:22,005
在工厂运作前摧毁它
