400
00:32:53,343 --> 00:32:54,411
早安
Morning.

401
00:32:55,011 --> 00:32:57,180
欢迎参加特训营
Welcome to your special training detachment.

402
00:32:57,313 --> 00:32:58,381
坐下来
Be seated.

403
00:32:59,082 --> 00:33:01,685
我是贝兹少将，航空作战中心指挥官
I'm Admiral Bates NAWDC commander.

404
00:33:01,818 --> 00:33:03,420
你们都是扞卫小组毕业生
You're all TOPGUN graduates.

405
00:33:04,187 --> 00:33:05,522
顶尖飞行员
The elite.

406
00:33:05,655 --> 00:33:07,657
菁英中的菁英
The best of the best.

407
00:33:08,158 --> 00:33:09,926
那是过去式
That was yesterday.

408
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:14,964
敌人全新的第五代战机赶上我们
The enemy's new fifth-generation
fighter has leveled the playing field.

409
00:33:15,098 --> 00:33:16,866
