His exploits are legendary.

420
00:33:45,995 --> 00:33:47,964
而且是这项计划有史以来
And he's considered to be one of the finest pilots

421
00:33:48,098 --> 00:33:50,100
训练出来最优秀的飞行员
this program has ever produced.

422
00:33:51,601 --> 00:33:53,069
他能够教导你们的
What he has to teach you

423
00:33:53,203 --> 00:33:56,706
