I give you Captain Pete Mitchell.

425
00:34:00,276 --> 00:34:02,979
呼号是独行侠
Call sign: "Maverick."

426
00:34:07,717 --> 00:34:08,718
早安
Good morning.

427
00:34:16,926 --> 00:34:18,762
F-18战机训练及标准操作程序
The F-18 NATOPS.

428
00:34:20,263 --> 00:34:23,900
包含了你们应该知道的一切
It contains everything they want you
to know about your aircraft.

429
00:34:24,901 --> 00:34:27,570
我猜你们都背得滚瓜烂熟
I'm assuming you know the book inside and out.

430
00:34:27,671 --> 00:34:28,972
-没错
-一定要的
-Damn right.
-Damn straight.

431
00:34:29,105 --> 00:34:30,106
你说得对
You got it.

432
00:34:38,148 --> 00:34:39,783
敌人也都知道
So does your enemy.

433
00:34:40,283 --> 00:34:41,918
他又来了
And we're off.

434
00:34:42,952 --> 00:34:45,955
敌人不知道的…是你们的极限
But what the enemy doesn't know is your limits.

435
00:34:46,956 --> 00:34:48,591
我打算找到它们
I intend to find them

436
00:34:48,692 --> 00:34:50,260
