公鸡
Rooster.

441
00:35:08,078 --> 00:35:08,945
布雷德利
Bradley.

442
00:35:09,679 --> 00:35:11,381
布雷德萧中尉
Lieutenant Bradshaw!

443
00:35:13,383 --> 00:35:14,384
是，长官
Yes sir.

444
00:35:15,385 --> 00:35:17,020
我们之间没必要这样
Let's not do it like this.

445
00:35:18,021 --> 00:35:19,289
你会把我刷下来吗？
You gonna wash me out?

446
00:35:21,024 --> 00:35:22,692
那要看你，不是看我
That'll be up to you not me.

447
00:35:25,028 --> 00:35:26,296
我可以走了吗？
Am I dismissed?

448
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:46,249
早安，飞行员，我是你们的上校
Good morning aviators. This is your captain speaking.

449
00:35:46,383 --> 00:35:48,485
欢迎参加基本飞行训练
Welcome to basic fighter maneuvers.

450
00:35:49,919 --> 00:35:52,856
今天要演练空中缠斗
As briefed today's exercise is dogfighting.

451
00:35:52,989 --> 00:35:54,758
只用机关枪，不用飞弹
Guns only no missiles.

452
00:35:55,759 --> 00:35:58,895
限低不能低于五千尺
We do not go below the hard deck of 5000 feet.

453
00:35:59,029 --> 00:36:01,898
两架战机一组，将我击落，否则…
Working as a team you have to shoot me down or else.

454
00:36:02,032 --> 00:36:05,201
-否则怎样？
-我会反击
-Or else what sir?
-Or else I shoot back.

455
00:36:05,335 --> 00:36:08,204
只要击落一架战机，两架都算输
If I shoot either one of you down you both lose.

456
00:36:08,338 --> 00:36:10,140
这家伙太臭屁了
This guy needs an ego check.

457
00:36:10,273 --> 00:36:11,675
我们会让他吃瘪
We'll see to that.

458
00:36:11,775 --> 00:36:14,377
-不如来赌一把
-你想赌什么？
-What say we put some skin in the game?
-What do you have in mind?

459
00:36:14,511 --> 00:36:17,347
先被击落做两百下伏地挺身
Whoever gets shot down first has to do 200 push-ups.

460
00:36:17,447 --> 00:36:20,116
大伙儿，很多下耶
Guys. That's a lot of push-ups.

461
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:22,385
训练不是叫假的，长官
They don't call it an exercise for nothing sir.

462
00:36:22,519 --> 00:36:24,387
那就一言为定
You got yourself a deal gentlemen.

463
00:36:24,521 --> 00:36:26,890
开战了，拼了啦
Fight's on. Let's turn and burn.

464
00:36:28,391 --> 00:36:29,693
粉弟，看到他吗？
Fanboy you see him?

465
00:36:29,793 --> 00:36:32,762
他不在前方，一定在后面
Nothing on radar up ahead. He must be somewhere behind us.

466
00:36:35,298 --> 00:36:36,800
-可恶
-搞什么？
-Damn it!
-What the hell?

467
00:36:36,933 --> 00:36:37,967
该死！
Shit!

468
00:36:42,605 --> 00:36:43,406
别这么冲，独行侠
Easy Maverick.

469
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:46,609
别在第一天就被炒鱿鱼
Let's try not to get fired on the first day.

470
00:36:46,743 --> 00:36:49,612
看见目标…独行侠逼近，向左急转
Tally tally tally! Maverick's coming in! Break left!

471
00:36:49,746 --> 00:36:50,947
向左急转
Breaking left.

472
00:36:52,949 --> 00:36:54,984
复仇者，你的僚机呢？
Payback where's your wingman?

473
00:36:55,118 --> 00:36:57,120
-公鸡，你在哪？
-我会罩你
-Rooster where are you?
-I got your back.

474
00:36:57,253 --> 00:36:59,823
我来了，撑着点，撑着点
I'm coming. Hang in there. Hang in there.

475
00:36:59,956 --> 00:37:01,124
快点，兄弟！快点
Hurry up man! Hurry up!

476
00:37:05,095 --> 00:37:07,063
-复仇者，向右急转
-向右急转
-Payback break right.
-Breaking right.

477
00:37:08,264 --> 00:37:11,768
公鸡救了你们，但他会付出代价
Rooster just saved your life fellas. But it's gonna cost him.

478
00:37:11,901 --> 00:37:13,436
这次不会，老头
Not this time old man.

479
00:37:16,006 --> 00:37:17,807
别被他激怒，独行侠
Don't let him get to you Maverick.

480
00:37:24,781 --> 00:37:27,283
公鸡，你飞得太低，快爬升 你快到限低了
Rooster you're too low! Pull up! You're hitting the hard deck!

481
00:37:27,417 --> 00:37:30,020
-高度，高度
-惨了
-Altitude. Altitude.
-Oh shit.

