-你死了
-可恶
-Smoked.
-Damn it.

492
00:38:03,386 --> 00:38:05,955
刚才自拍得很爽嘛，伏低
It was all fun and games in that selfie wasn't it? Down!

493
00:38:06,056 --> 00:38:06,823
嘿，凤凰
Say Phoenix.

494
00:38:06,956 --> 00:38:09,993
不如告诉大家“巴布”是别的小名
How's about we tell everybody "Bob" stands for something?

495
00:38:10,126 --> 00:38:12,228
-不只是罗勃特
-别上当
-Other than Robert I mean.
-Don't take the bait Bob.

496
00:38:12,362 --> 00:38:14,397
想知道他为什么叫刽子手吗？
Want to know why we call him Hangman?

497
00:38:14,531 --> 00:38:16,866
我想到了，“巴布叭噗”
I got it. "Baby On Board."

498
00:38:19,135 --> 00:38:20,704
靠！
Shit!

499
00:38:22,072 --> 00:38:23,973
各位飞官好，开战了
Greetings aviators. Fight's on.

500
00:38:24,507 --> 00:38:26,810
凤凰，把这家伙击落
All right Phoenix let's take this guy out!

501
00:38:26,910 --> 00:38:27,877
小心后方，凤凰
Watch your back Phoenix.

502
00:38:28,011 --> 00:38:30,080
-向右急转
-向右急转
-Break right!
-Breaking right.

503
00:38:32,382 --> 00:38:33,350
他去哪儿？
Where's he going?

504
00:38:33,483 --> 00:38:36,553
他是刽子手，只会害死你
That's why we call him Hangman.
He'll always hang you out to dry.

505
00:38:37,554 --> 00:38:38,888
丢下你的僚机
Leaving your wingman.

506
00:38:39,022 --> 00:38:40,857
很久没看过这一招了
There's a strategy I haven't seen in a while.

507
00:38:40,990 --> 00:38:43,226
他在笑你，你忍得了吗？
He called you a man Phoenix. You gonna take that?

508
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,861
只要他当你就忍得了
So long as he doesn't call you a man.

509
00:38:44,994 --> 00:38:46,896
巴布，独行侠在哪？
Talk to me Bob. Where's Maverick?

510
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,999
天啊，他已经绕回来了！
Jesus his nose is already coming around!

511
00:38:49,099 --> 00:38:50,367
帮我甩掉他，刽子手
Get him off me Hangman!

512
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:54,404
各位听众，我要埋了这化石
For all you folks at home this is how you bury a fossil.

513
00:38:54,537 --> 00:38:57,040
