that it may never be airworthy again.

1096
01:23:00,917 --> 01:23:03,053
冰人不能再保护你了
Iceman is no longer here to protect you.

1097
01:23:04,087 --> 01:23:06,556
我大可以把你送去军事法庭
I have everything I need to have you court-martialed

1098
01:23:06,690 --> 01:23:08,391
让你不荣誉退伍
and dishonorably discharged.

1099
01:23:09,159 --> 01:23:10,593
我该怎么做？
So what do I do?

1100
01:23:11,594 --> 01:23:14,764
冒着飞行员阵亡和任务失败的风险
Risk the lives of my pilots and
perhaps the success of this mission

1101
01:23:16,166 --> 01:23:17,167
或是
or...

1102
01:23:18,835 --> 01:23:20,170
拿我的军旅生涯赌一把
risk my career

1103
01:23:21,271 --> 01:23:22,939
任命你为任务队长？
by appointing you team leader?

1104
01:23:26,376 --> 01:23:27,377
长官…
Sir--

1105
01:23:27,510 --> 01:23:31,047
中将只是问问而已，上校
I think the admiral's asking a rhetorical question Captain.

1106
01:25:12,048 --> 01:25:13,550
该怎么办？呆头鹅
Talk to me Goose.

1107
01:25:16,987 --> 01:25:18,355
米契尔上校
Captain Mitchell!

1108
01:25:25,328 --> 01:25:27,097
你属于这里
You're where you belong.

1109
01:25:32,068 --> 01:25:33,470
让我们以你为荣
Make us proud.

1110
01:25:59,562 --> 01:26:01,731
很荣幸能与你们飞行
It has been an honor flying with you.

1111
01:26:02,832 --> 01:26:06,136
每一位都是菁英中的菁英
Each one of you represents the best of the best.

1112
01:26:07,103 --> 01:26:09,773
这项任务非常艰钜
This is a very specific mission.

1113
01:26:10,774 --> 01:26:13,944
我的选择完全是针对任务
My choice is a reflection of that and nothing more.

1114
01:26:14,077 --> 01:26:15,879
挑选两组F小队队员
Choose your two Foxtrot teams.

1115
01:26:17,347 --> 01:26:19,115
复仇者和粉弟
Payback and Fanboy.

1116
01:26:19,950 --> 01:26:21,418
凤凰和巴布
Phoenix and Bob.

1117
01:26:25,755 --> 01:26:27,123
你的僚机驾驶员
And your wingman.

1118
01:26:31,895 --> 01:26:32,896
公鸡
Rooster.

1119
01:26:37,300 --> 01:26:39,636
其他人在航母待命
The rest of you will stand by on the carrier

1120
01:26:39,769 --> 01:26:42,606
随时准备支援
for any reserve role that's required.

1121
01:26:43,440 --> 01:26:44,641
解散
Dismissed.

1122
01:26:52,415 --> 01:26:55,251
你们的目标是迫切的威胁
Your target is a clear and present threat.

1123
01:26:56,886 --> 01:27:00,657
受到敌国掌控的秘密铀浓缩工厂
A secret uranium enrichment site under rogue state control.

1124
01:27:01,157 --> 01:27:02,626
位于地下碉堡
It's an underground bunker

1125
01:27:02,759 --> 01:27:04,494
坐落在这两座山脉之间
tucked between these two mountains.

1126
01:27:06,062 --> 01:27:09,799
进攻航道受到多个防空炮台防卫
Your route of ingress is heavily
defended by surface-to-air missiles

1127
01:27:09,933 --> 01:27:12,302
另有第五代战机支援
backed up by fifth-generation fighters.

1128
01:27:12,435 --> 01:27:15,071
F-18攻击小队一旦跨越边界
Once your F-18 strike team crosses the border

1129
01:27:15,171 --> 01:27:17,140
雷伊泰号航空母舰
Tomahawk missiles from the USS Leyte Gulf

1130
01:27:17,274 --> 01:27:21,077
就会同步发射战斧飞弹攻击这座机场
will launch a synchronized strike
on the enemy's airfield here.

1131
01:27:22,178 --> 01:27:24,447
炸毁那里的跑道
This will knock out their runway.

1132
01:27:26,116 --> 01:27:29,653
但你们还得对付已经升空的战机
But you'll have to contend with any planes already in the air.

1133
01:27:29,786 --> 01:27:32,589
战斧飞弹击中后，敌方就知道你们来了
The moment those Tomahawks hit
the enemy will know you're coming.

1134
01:27:33,823 --> 01:27:37,927
抵达目标时间是2分30秒
Your time to target will be two minutes and 30 seconds.

1135
01:27:39,496 --> 01:27:41,464
超过时间就会遭到
Any longer than that and you will be exposed

1136
01:27:41,598 --> 01:27:44,134
没被击中的战机攻击
