1137
01:27:47,637 --> 01:27:50,140
这是你们受训的目的
This is what you've all been training for.

1138
01:27:52,108 --> 01:27:53,476
安全回来
Come home safely.

1139
01:28:08,024 --> 01:28:09,993
让他们好看
You give 'em hell!

1140
01:28:22,539 --> 01:28:23,540
长官
Sir.

1141
01:28:23,907 --> 01:28:24,908
长官？
Sir?

1142
01:28:27,243 --> 01:28:28,244
我…
I...

1143
01:28:31,147 --> 01:28:32,916
我只想说…
I just want to say--

1144
01:28:42,025 --> 01:28:43,193
等安全回来…
We'll talk

1145
01:28:44,828 --> 01:28:46,029
我们再聊
when we get back.

1146
01:28:52,369 --> 01:28:54,104
嘿，布雷德利！布雷德利
Hey Bradley! Bradley!

1147
01:28:55,071 --> 01:28:56,072
嘿
Hey.

1148
01:28:59,709 --> 01:29:00,944
你行的
You got this.

1149
01:29:09,519 --> 01:29:10,520
独行侠
Maverick.

1150
01:29:12,856 --> 01:29:13,623
独行侠？
Maverick?

1151
01:29:15,558 --> 01:29:17,460
你在吧？
Hey you with me?

1152
01:29:18,962 --> 01:29:20,964
我不喜欢那副表情
I don't like that look Mav.

1153
01:29:23,767 --> 01:29:25,135
我只有这一号表情
It's the only one I got.

1154
01:29:29,940 --> 01:29:31,107
谢谢你
Thank you.

1155
01:29:32,742 --> 01:29:34,811
要是我不能再见到你，宏多…
If I don't see you again Hondo

1156
01:29:34,945 --> 01:29:36,112
谢谢你
thank you.

1157
01:29:44,087 --> 01:29:45,889
这是我的荣幸，上校
It's been an honor Captain.

1158
01:30:18,955 --> 01:30:21,825
匕首一号，准备弹射
Dagger One up and ready on Catapult One.

1159
01:30:21,958 --> 01:30:24,127
匕首候补，待命中
Dagger Spare standing by.

1160
01:30:24,261 --> 01:30:25,962
匕首四号，准备好了
Dagger Four up and ready.

1161
01:30:26,096 --> 01:30:27,664
匕首三号，准备好了
Dagger Three up and ready.

1162
01:30:27,797 --> 01:30:29,966
匕首二号，准备好了
Dagger Two up and ready.

1163
01:30:30,934 --> 01:30:33,770
支援军机起飞，攻击小队准备好了
Support assets airborne. Strike package ready.

1164
01:30:33,870 --> 01:30:35,705
等待起飞指令
Standing by for launch decision.

1165
01:30:36,273 --> 01:30:37,274
出发
Send them.

1166
01:30:58,028 --> 01:30:59,162
匕首二号，起飞
Dagger Two away.

1167
01:31:00,163 --> 01:31:02,132
匕首三号，起飞
Dagger Three away.

1168
01:31:02,832 --> 01:31:04,134
匕首四号，起飞
Dagger Four away.

1169
01:31:15,145 --> 01:31:17,681
侦察机，匕首一号报到
Comanche Dagger One. Standby check in.

1170
01:31:19,149 --> 01:31:20,417
侦察机就定位
Comanche 11 set.

1171
01:31:20,550 --> 01:31:22,886
空域安全，建议匕首小队继续任务
Picture clean. Recommend Dagger continue.

1172
01:31:23,019 --> 01:31:24,921
收到，匕首小队低空飞行
Copy. Daggers descending below radar.

1173
01:31:44,774 --> 01:31:47,377
匕首小队低于雷达，切换至鹰眼影像
Daggers now below radar. Switching to E-2 picture.

1174
01:31:56,052 --> 01:31:58,488
前方是敌方领地
Here we go. Enemy territory up ahead.

1175
01:31:58,622 --> 01:32:01,558
60秒后登陆，控制中心，回报状况
Feet dry in 60 seconds. Comanche Dagger One. Picture.

1176
01:32:01,691 --> 01:32:04,394
前方安全，你的决定
Comanche. Picture clean. Decision is yours.

1177
01:32:04,494 --> 01:32:05,895
收到
Copy.

1178
01:32:13,970 --> 01:32:15,138
展开攻击
Dagger attack.

1179
01:32:20,510 --> 01:32:21,878
战斧飞弹已经发射
Tomahawks airborne.

1180
01:32:21,978 --> 01:32:24,114
没有回头路了
No turning back now.

1181
01:32:29,786 --> 01:32:31,888
匕首小队，组成进攻队形
Daggers assume attack formation.

1182
01:32:40,964 --> 01:32:42,933
组队飞向目标
Daggers set. Proceeding to target.

1183
01:32:43,066 --> 01:32:47,470
2分30秒，三、二、一…计时开始
Two minutes and 30 seconds in three two one mark.

1184
01:32:47,604 --> 01:32:48,972
-二号计时开始
-三号计时开始
-Two mark.
-Three mark.

1185
01:32:49,105 --> 01:32:49,906
四号计时开始
Four mark.

1186
01:32:54,844 --> 01:32:55,779
进入峡谷
Going in.

1187
01:33:11,328 --> 01:33:13,563
飞过第一个炮台
First SAM site overhead.

1188
01:33:18,101 --> 01:33:19,636
我们没被雷达侦测到
Looks like we're clear on radar Mav.

1189
01:33:19,769 --> 01:33:21,271
别掉以轻心
Let's not take it for granted.

1190
01:33:24,874 --> 01:33:27,143
更多炮台，三点钟方向
More SAMs! Three o'clock high!

1191
01:33:29,312 --> 01:33:31,715
-两分钟后抵达目标
-收到
-We got two minutes to target.
-Copy.

1192
01:33:31,848 --> 01:33:34,017
我们落后几秒，公鸡，得快点
We're a few seconds behind Rooster. We got to move.

1193
01:33:35,719 --> 01:33:38,555
战斧飞弹30秒后击中跑道
Thirty seconds to Tomahawk impact on enemy airstrip.

1194
01:33:47,030 --> 01:33:47,998
匕首小队
Dagger Comanche.

1195
01:33:48,131 --> 01:33:50,066
我们侦测到两架敌机
We're picking up two bandits. Single group two contacts.

1196
01:33:50,200 --> 01:33:52,902
-它们从哪来的？
-长程巡逻？
-Where the hell'd they come from?
-Long-range patrol?

1197
01:33:57,907 --> 01:33:59,509
它们的航向是什么？
Comanche what's their heading?

1198
01:33:59,609 --> 01:34:01,978
航向090，目标西南50哩
Bull's-eye 090 50 tacked southwest.

1199
01:34:02,078 --> 01:34:04,180
它们没看到我们，飞走了
They're headed away from us. They don't know we're here.

1200
01:34:04,314 --> 01:34:06,216
战斧飞弹一击中空军基地
The second those Tomahawks hit the air base

1201
01:34:06,349 --> 01:34:08,551
敌机就会折返防卫目标
those bandits are gonna move to defend the target.

1202
01:34:08,685 --> 01:34:11,187
我们得抢先一步，加速
We have to get there before they do. Increase speed.

1203
01:34:12,589 --> 01:34:14,991
我们会跟上，别等我
We got you Mav. Don't wait for me.

1204
01:34:20,931 --> 01:34:23,900
匕首二号和四号进度落后
Sir Daggers Two and Four are behind schedule.

1205
01:34:24,034 --> 01:34:26,036
抵达目标时间，1分20秒
Time to target one minute 20.

1206
01:34:27,070 --> 01:34:29,272
战斧飞弹将于三、二…
Tomahawk impact in three two...

1207
01:34:33,743 --> 01:34:36,079
击中目标，机场跑道全毁
Impact. Enemy runway is destroyed.

1208
01:34:37,080 --> 01:34:38,648
他们知道我们来了
They know we're coming now.

1209
01:34:42,118 --> 01:34:44,287
敌机转向前去保护目标
Bandits are switching course to defend the target.

1210
01:34:44,421 --> 01:34:45,555
公鸡，你在哪里？
Rooster where are you?

1211
01:34:47,223 --> 01:34:48,892
快点，敌机来袭
Come on Rooster. Bandits inbound.

1212
01:34:49,025 --> 01:34:51,227
我们得赶上，快加速
We got to make up time now. Let's turn and burn.

1213
01:34:59,135 --> 01:35:00,203
小心，凤凰
Heads up Phoenix.

1214
01:35:10,146 --> 01:35:14,417
敌机距离目标两分钟，匕首小队一分钟
Sir bandits are two minutes from target.

1215
01:35:12,730 --> 01:35:14,410
Daggers are one minute from target.

1216
01:35:14,551 --> 01:35:16,920
快啊，公鸡，不快点就会死
Come on Rooster. Move it or lose it.

1217
01:35:18,955 --> 01:35:21,992
我们落后了，真的得加速
Guys we're falling behind. We really got to move.

1218
01:35:22,125 --> 01:35:23,827
现在不加速
If we don't increase our speed right now

1219
01:35:23,960 --> 01:35:26,696
敌机就会在目标那里等着我们
those bandits are gonna be waiting for us
when we reach the target.

1220
01:35:28,465 --> 01:35:29,699
爸，该怎么做？
Talk to me Dad.

1221
01:35:31,134 --> 01:35:33,470
加油，你行的，别犹豫
Come on kid you can do it.

1222
01:35:33,603 --> 01:35:34,671
放手去做
Don't think just do.

1223
01:35:43,013 --> 01:35:44,614
天啊，别那么快
Jesus Rooster not that fast!

1224
01:35:44,714 --> 01:35:47,150
这就对了，咱们上吧
That's it kid that's it. All right let's go.

1225
