30秒后抵达目标，巴布，检查雷射
Thirty seconds to target. Bob check your laser.

1229
01:36:05,936 --> 01:36:09,539
检查完毕，确认雷射辨识码1688
Air-to-ground check complete. Laser code verified 1688.

1230
01:36:09,673 --> 01:36:10,740
雷射待命中
Laser is a go!

1231
01:36:12,976 --> 01:36:14,444
小心
Watch your heads.

1232
01:36:16,112 --> 01:36:17,647
哇靠
Holy shit!

1233
01:36:17,747 --> 01:36:19,649
-复仇者，跟上了吗？
-在你后方
-Payback you with me?
-Right behind you.

1234
01:36:20,750 --> 01:36:22,519
凤凰，准备攻击
Phoenix stand by for pop-up strike.

1235
01:36:22,652 --> 01:36:24,054
匕首三号就位
Dagger Three in position.

1236
01:36:24,654 --> 01:36:27,223
倒数三、二、一，爬升
Popping in three two one.

1237
01:36:55,318 --> 01:36:57,654
-标示目标，巴布
-匕首三号
-Get me eyes on that target Bob.
-Dagger Three.

1238
01:36:58,655 --> 01:36:59,756
待命
Stand by Mav.

1239
01:36:59,889 --> 01:37:02,192
-快啊，巴布
-待命
-Come on Bob come on.
-Stand by.

1240
01:37:02,892 --> 01:37:05,595
-标示目标了
-锁定目标，投掷炸弹
-I've got it. Captured!
