Dagger Two status.

1244
01:37:34,057 --> 01:37:35,692
就快到了，独行侠，就快到了
Almost there Mav. Almost there.

1245
01:37:38,428 --> 01:37:40,030
粉弟，雷射咧？
Fanboy where's my laser?

1246
01:37:40,463 --> 01:37:42,565
雷射出了状况
Rooster there's something wrong with this laser.

1247
01:37:42,699 --> 01:37:44,234
靠，雷射失灵…
Shit! Deadeye deadeye deadeye!

1248
