Deploying countermeasures.

1270
01:39:17,994 --> 01:39:19,629
我没被击中
Negative contact.

1271
01:39:21,698 --> 01:39:22,799
匕首一号进行回避
Dagger One defending.

1272
01:39:24,067 --> 01:39:26,903
-回报状况，巴布
-凤凰、独行侠，向右急转
-Talk to me Bob.
-Break right Phoenix! Break right! Mav!

1273
01:39:27,037 --> 01:39:28,672
九点钟方向！九点钟方向
Nine o'clock! Nine o'clock!

1274
01:39:29,472 --> 01:39:31,374
公鸡，两枚在你正后方
Rooster two more on your six.

1275
01:39:31,508 --> 01:39:33,076
匕首二号发射诱弹
Dagger Two defending.

1276
01:39:37,547 --> 01:39:39,950
-复仇者，正前方
-发射诱弹
-Payback SAM on your nose.
-Dagger Four defending.

1277
01:39:40,083 --> 01:39:41,551
-七点钟方向
-回报状况，巴布
-Rooster tally seven o'clock!
-Talk to me Bob!

1278
01:39:41,685 --> 01:39:42,852
-正后方
-匕首二号发射诱弹
-On our six!
-Dagger Two defending.

1279
01:39:42,953 --> 01:39:44,821
-向右急转
-我看到了
-Phoenix break right!
-I see it!

1280
01:39:45,188 --> 01:39:47,090
我看到了
I see it, i see it.

1281
01:39:51,962 --> 01:39:53,430
匕首二号发射诱弹
Dagger Two defending.

1282
01:39:54,931 --> 01:39:56,032
靠，我没诱弹了
Shit I'm out of flares!

1283
01:39:56,166 --> 01:39:57,934
公鸡，回避
Rooster evade evade!

1284
01:39:58,535 --> 01:40:00,837
甩不掉它们！它们锁定我了 它们锁定我了
I can't shake 'em! They're on me! They're on me!

1285
01:40:10,981 --> 01:40:12,549
独行侠，不！
Mav! No!

1286
01:40:14,684 --> 01:40:17,921
匕首一号中弹，重复，匕首一号中弹
Dagger One is hit! I repeat Dagger One is hit!

1287
01:40:18,054 --> 01:40:19,623
独行侠被击落
Maverick is down.

1288
01:40:19,756 --> 01:40:20,924
匕首一号，回报
Dagger One status.

1289
01:40:21,057 --> 01:40:22,592
回报！
Status!

1290
01:40:22,726 --> 01:40:24,894
有谁看到他？
Anyone see him? Does anyone see him?

1291
01:40:24,995 --> 01:40:26,997
-匕首一号，回报
-没看到降落伞
-Dagger One come in!
-I didn't see a parachute.

1292
01:40:27,130 --> 01:40:28,898
我们得绕回去
We have to circle back.

1293
01:40:28,999 --> 01:40:31,401
敌机来袭，准备攻击
Comanche. Bandits inbound. Single group hot.

1294
01:40:31,534 --> 01:40:33,103
建议匕首小队往南飞
Recommend Dagger flow south.

1295
01:40:33,937 --> 01:40:35,939
一分钟后拦截
One minute to intercept.

1296
01:40:38,975 --> 01:40:40,710
快叫他们飞返航母
Get 'em back to the carrier now.

1297
01:40:40,810 --> 01:40:43,213
敌机来袭，匕首小队飞返基地
All Daggers flow to ECP. You have bandits headed for you.

1298
01:40:43,313 --> 01:40:44,381
独行侠呢？
What about Maverick?

1299
01:40:44,481 --> 01:40:47,450
跟他说他也无能为力，F-18打不过敌机
Tell him there's nothing he can do
for Maverick not in a goddamn F-18.

1300
01:40:47,584 --> 01:40:50,387
匕首后备要求进行空中支援
Dagger Spare request permission to launch and fly air cover.

1301
01:40:52,756 --> 01:40:53,757
不准
Negative Spare.

1302
01:40:54,958 --> 01:40:57,394
-展开搜救行动
-不行，空中有敌机
-Launch search and rescue.
-Negative. Not with bandits in the air.

1303
01:40:57,494 --> 01:41:00,931
-独行侠还活着
-今天不能再损失任何人
-But sir Maverick is still out there.
-We are not losing anyone else today.

1304
01:41:03,133 --> 01:41:04,501
命令他们回来
Get 'em home now.

1305
01:41:04,634 --> 01:41:07,037
匕首小队，不准救援
Dagger you are not to engage.

1306
01:41:07,170 --> 01:41:09,239
重复，不准救援
Repeat do not engage.

1307
01:41:09,339 --> 01:41:12,442
匕首二号飞返航母，确认
Dagger Two return to carrier. Acknowledge.

1308
01:41:12,575 --> 01:41:13,510
确认
Acknowledge.

1309
01:41:13,643 --> 01:41:17,147
公鸡，敌机逼近，不能回去
Rooster those bandits are closing. We can't go back.

1310
01:41:17,280 --> 01:41:19,950
公鸡，他死了
Rooster he's gone.

1311
01:41:21,785 --> 01:41:23,153
独行侠死了
Maverick's gone.

1312
01:42:53,743 --> 01:42:54,744
噢，不…
Oh no no.

1313
01:43:01,451 --> 01:43:03,053
匕首二号被击中
Dagger Two is hit.

1314
01:43:04,020 --> 01:43:05,088
匕首二号被击中
Dagger Two is hit.

1315
01:43:06,856 --> 01:43:08,058
匕首二号，回报
Dagger Two come in.

1316
01:43:09,926 --> 01:43:11,728
匕首二号，收到吗？
Dagger Two do you copy?

1317
01:43:12,462 --> 01:43:14,631
匕首二号，回报
Dagger Two come in.

1318
01:43:40,056 --> 01:43:40,991
你没事吧？
You all right?

1319
01:43:41,124 --> 01:43:42,892
我没事，你呢？
Yeah I'm good. You all right?

1320
01:43:45,328 --> 01:43:46,429
搞什么鬼？
What the hell?

1321
01:43:46,563 --> 01:43:48,798
-你来干嘛？
-我来干嘛？
-What are you doing here?
-What am I doing here?

1322
01:43:48,932 --> 01:43:51,334
我替你挡飞弹不是让你也落难
You think I took that missile
so you could be down here with me?

1323
01:43:51,468 --> 01:43:53,270
你早就该飞返航母了
You should be back on the carrier by now!

1324
01:43:53,403 --> 01:43:54,771
我救了你一命
I saved your life!

1325
01:43:54,904 --> 01:43:58,208
我救了你，那才是重点
I saved your life. That's the whole point.

1326
01:43:58,341 --> 01:44:00,210
你到底在想什么？
What the hell were you even thinking?

1327
01:44:00,343 --> 01:44:02,212
你叫我不要想
You told me not to think!

1328
01:44:18,929 --> 01:44:20,030
这样嘛…
Well

1329
01:44:21,464 --> 01:44:22,933
见到你真好
it's good to see you.

1330
01:44:25,201 --> 01:44:26,970
我也是
It's good to see you too.

1331
01:44:31,041 --> 01:44:32,342
有什么计划？
So what's the plan?

1332
01:44:43,320 --> 01:44:44,788
不是吧
You're not serious.

1333
01:45:00,170 --> 01:45:01,972
你在开玩笑吧
You've got to be shitting me.

1334
01:45:03,974 --> 01:45:05,008
F-14战机？
An F-14?

1335
01:45:05,675 --> 01:45:07,377
我开那玩意击落三架米格机
I shot down three MiGs in one of those.

1336
01:45:07,510 --> 01:45:10,046
那古董能不能飞都不知道
We don't even know if that bag of ass can fly.

1337
01:45:12,682 --> 01:45:14,651
-试试就知道
-独行侠
-Let's find out.
-Mav!

1338
01:45:16,486 --> 01:45:17,487
好吧
Okay.

1339
01:45:27,097 --> 01:45:29,099
-前面有人
-是啊
-There's guys up there Mav.
-Yeah.

1340
01:45:30,200 --> 01:45:32,102
-那里有更多人
-好吧
-There's more over there.
-Okay.

1341
01:45:33,503 --> 01:45:35,705
-开始跑吧
-好啊，跑，跑啊
-Let's start running.
-Yeah run. Run.

1342
01:45:45,048 --> 01:45:47,517
我会打信号要你充气
Once I give you the signal for air

1343
01:45:48,118 --> 01:45:51,021
打开这开关直到针头指到120
you're gonna flip this switch until the needle gets to 120.

1344
01:45:51,121 --> 01:45:52,088
引擎启动后
When the engine starts

1345
01:45:52,222 --> 01:45:54,791
马上拔除一切
you got to pull out the pins and disconnect everything.

1346
01:45:54,925 --> 01:45:56,526
-你了吗？
-我了
-You understand?
-Yeah.

1347
01:45:58,728 --> 01:45:59,729
好耶！
Yes!

1348
01:46:01,564 --> 01:46:03,767
我一上去就收起梯子
Once I'm up stow the ladder.

1349
01:46:11,641 --> 01:46:13,743
好吧，哇塞
Okay. Wow.

1350
01:46:14,945 --> 01:46:16,746
很久没开了
It's been a minute huh Mav?

1351
01:46:45,575 --> 01:46:48,511
天啊，这玩意超老旧的
Oh my God. This thing is so old.

1352
01:46:49,512 --> 01:46:50,513
好吧
All right.

1353
01:46:55,619 --> 01:46:57,087
-关闭座舱罩
-好
-Canopy?
-Clear.

1354
01:47:15,338 --> 01:47:17,207
两条跑道都被炸毁
Both runways are cratered.

1355
01:47:18,108 --> 01:47:19,976
该怎么让这老古董起飞？
How we gonna get this museum piece in the air?

1356
01:47:30,387 --> 01:47:31,955
你为什么延展机翼？
Why are the wings coming out Mav?

1357
01:47:38,528 --> 01:47:41,164
这是滑行道，不是跑道
Mav this is a taxiway not a runway.

1358
01:47:41,898 --> 01:47:44,968
而且是很短的滑行道
This is a very short taxiway Mav.

1359
01:47:45,068 --> 01:47:45,902
坐好了
Just hang on.

1360
01:47:47,571 --> 01:47:48,805
哇咧！
Holy shit!

1361
01:47:54,878 --> 01:47:55,979
快点，快点
Come on come on come on.

1362
01:47:56,079 --> 01:47:57,147
指针能运作
Needle's alive.

1363
01:48:00,684 --> 01:48:02,986
-独行侠？
-很好，快点…
-Mav?
-That's it. Come on come on!

1364
01:48:03,086 --> 01:48:04,154
好吧
All right.

1365
01:48:05,055 --> 01:48:07,023
-独行侠
-起飞罗
-Mav!
-Here we go.

1366
01:48:08,358 --> 01:48:09,859
天啊
Holy shit.

1367
01:48:23,573 --> 01:48:26,676
长官，收到公鸡的信号
Sir we're receiving a signal from Rooster's ESAT.

1368
01:48:26,776 --> 01:48:28,678
看起来是故障
But there seems to be a malfunction.

1369
01:48:28,778 --> 01:48:29,946
-信号又消失了？
-不是
-Have you lost him?
-No sir.

1370
01:48:30,947 --> 01:48:32,549
他进入超音速
He's supersonic.

1371
01:48:33,083 --> 01:48:34,184
他在飞行
He's airborne.

1372
01:48:35,485 --> 01:48:37,020
-用什么飞？
-长官
-In what?
-Sir.

1373
01:48:37,887 --> 01:48:41,925
侦察机回报一架F-14战机正在飞来
Overwatch reports an F-14 Tomcat is airborne
and on course for our position.

1374
01:48:43,093 --> 01:48:45,495
不可能，不可能
Can't be. It can't be!

1375
01:48:47,197 --> 01:48:48,131
是独行侠
Maverick.

1376
01:48:50,433 --> 01:48:52,869
公鸡，快联络航母
Okay Rooster get us in touch with the boat.

1377
01:48:52,969 --> 01:48:54,271
我正在试
I'm working on it.

1378
01:48:54,404 --> 01:48:57,941
无线电失效，没有雷达，一切都故障
Radio's out. No radar. Everything's dead back here.

1379
01:48:58,508 --> 01:49:00,977
-教我怎么做
-先是无线电
-What do I do? Talk me through it.
-Okay first the radio.

1380
01:49:01,111 --> 01:49:02,078
打开…
Throw the...

1381
01:49:03,113 --> 01:49:05,081
UHF-2断路器
the UHF-2 circuit breaker.

1382
01:49:05,215 --> 01:49:06,216
试试看
Try that.

1383
01:49:06,950 --> 01:49:09,252
有一大堆断路器，哪一个？
There's 300 breakers back here. Anything more specific?

1384
01:49:09,386 --> 01:49:11,321
不知道，那是你爸的领域
I don't know. That was your dad's department.

1385
01:49:11,454 --> 01:49:12,989
我会想办法
I'll figure it out.

1386
01:49:16,159 --> 01:49:18,228
两架敌机在底下五点钟方向
Mav tally two 5:00 low.

1387
01:49:23,833 --> 01:49:24,968
该怎么办？
What do we do?

1388
01:49:25,535 --> 01:49:27,904
听好，冷静点
Okay listen. Just be cool.

1389
01:49:28,004 --> 01:49:29,806
我们若是暴露了身分早就死了
If they knew who we were we'd be dead already.

1390
01:49:31,975 --> 01:49:33,944
他们来了
Well here they come.

1391
01:49:34,778 --> 01:49:37,147
-有什么打算？
-戴上面罩
-What's your plan?
-Just put your mask on.

1392
01:49:38,448 --> 01:49:40,850
记住，我们是同一国的
Remember we're on the same team.

1393
01:49:43,520 --> 01:49:45,288
挥手和微笑
Just wave and smile.

1394
01:49:46,022 --> 01:49:47,557
挥手和微笑
Just wave and smile.

1395
01:49:54,764 --> 01:49:56,466
那什么信号？他在说什么？
What's that signal? What's he saying?

1396
01:49:56,566 --> 01:49:59,469
我不知道他在说什么
No idea. I have no idea what he's saying.

1397
01:50:00,303 --> 01:50:03,773
-这个咧？
-我也没看过
-What about that one? Any idea?
-No never seen that one either.

1398
01:50:06,977 --> 01:50:11,014
靠，他的僚机进入攻击位置
Oh shit. His wingman is moving into weapons envelope.

1399
01:50:11,948 --> 01:50:13,116
听好了
All right listen up.

1400
01:50:13,216 --> 01:50:15,852
我一下令你就抓住头上的圆环
When I tell you you grab those rings above your head.

1401
01:50:15,986 --> 01:50:17,721
那是弹跳把手
That's the ejection handle.

1402
01:50:18,822 --> 01:50:21,024
不能逃离他们吗？
Mav can we outrun these guys?

1403
01:50:21,591 --> 01:50:23,226
他们有飞弹和机关枪
Not their missiles and guns.

1404
01:50:28,298 --> 01:50:29,733
那就要空战罗
Then it's a dogfight.

1405
01:50:30,367 --> 01:50:33,169
一架F-14…对上第五代战机？
An F-14 against fifth-gen fighters?

1406
01:50:34,871 --> 01:50:37,140
关键不在飞机，而是飞行员
It's not the plane it's the pilot.

1407
01:50:38,575 --> 01:50:40,543
我不在你肯定会迎敌
You'd go after 'em if I wasn't here.

1408
01:50:41,144 --> 01:50:42,979
但你在啊
But you are here.

1409
01:50:43,713 --> 01:50:45,148
拜托，独行侠
Come on Mav.

1410
01:50:46,049 --> 01:50:47,250
别犹豫
Don't think.

1411
01:50:48,618 --> 01:50:49,686
放手去做
Just do.

1412
01:51:05,201 --> 01:51:07,170
看到飞弹就告诉我
Tell me when you see smoke in the air.

1413
01:51:11,608 --> 01:51:13,743
-飞弹来袭！飞弹来袭
-坐好了
-Smoke in the air! Smoke in the air!
-Hang on.

1414
01:51:16,546 --> 01:51:18,915
好耶，击落了一架！击落了一架
Yeah Mav! Splash one! Splash one!

1415
01:51:24,354 --> 01:51:25,622
又来一枚飞弹
Here comes another one.

1416
01:51:28,925 --> 01:51:31,027
公鸡，发射诱弹
Rooster flares! Now now now!

1417
01:51:34,264 --> 01:51:35,565
分配气阀
Splitting the throttles.

1418
01:51:37,767 --> 01:51:38,902
绕回去
Coming around.

1419
01:51:43,106 --> 01:51:45,642
-快锁定，快锁定
-锁定了
-Give me tone give me tone.
-You got him Mav! You got him!

1420
01:51:45,775 --> 01:51:46,643
发射飞弹
Taking the shot.

1421
01:51:53,283 --> 01:51:54,584
搞什么？
What the--

1422
01:51:55,585 --> 01:51:57,754
哇咧，那是怎样？
Holy shit! What the fuck was that?

1423
01:51:59,055 --> 01:52:01,324
坐好了，我要低飞
Hang on. We got to get low.

1424
01:52:01,458 --> 01:52:03,793
峡谷会干扰他的瞄准器
The terrain will confuse his targeting system.

1425
01:52:05,962 --> 01:52:06,896
他来了
Here he comes!

1426
01:52:19,609 --> 01:52:21,645
回报状况，他在哪里？
Talk to me Rooster. Where is he?

1427
01:52:21,778 --> 01:52:23,179
他紧追不舍
He's still on us!

1428
01:52:30,420 --> 01:52:32,522
-我们被击中，被击中
-可恶
-We took a hit! We took a hit!
-Damn it!

1429
01:52:37,661 --> 01:52:39,930
-快秀一些你的招术
-坐好了
-Come on Mav. Do some of that pilot shit.
-Brace yourself.

1430
01:52:50,507 --> 01:52:51,541
哇咧
Holy shit.

1431
01:52:58,615 --> 01:53:00,383
锁定他，发射飞弹
I got tone. Taking the shot.

1432
01:53:04,988 --> 01:53:06,022
可恶
Damn it!

1433
01:53:07,023 --> 01:53:09,359
没飞弹了，改用机关枪
Out of missiles. Switching to guns.

1434
01:53:15,765 --> 01:53:16,967
快啊，快啊
Come on Mav come on.

1435
01:53:19,536 --> 01:53:21,071
-击中了，独行侠
-还没结束
-You got him Mav!
-It's not over yet.

1436
01:53:25,976 --> 01:53:27,744
-最后的机会
-你行的
-One last chance.
-You can do this.

1437
01:53:28,979 --> 01:53:30,013
加油
Come on Maverick.

1438
01:53:40,223 --> 01:53:41,992
好耶，击落第二架
Yes! Splash two!

1439
01:53:53,069 --> 01:53:54,938
-我修好无线电
-好样的
-Mav I got the radio on.
-Outstanding.

1440
01:53:55,071 --> 01:53:57,007
-呼叫航母
-收到
-Get us in touch with the boat.
-Copy that.

1441
01:53:59,276 --> 01:54:00,543
天啊
Oh my God.

1442
01:54:02,545 --> 01:54:04,114
这家伙在哪里？
Where the hell is this guy?

1443
01:54:05,548 --> 01:54:07,050
他在正前方
He's on our nose.

1444
01:54:10,553 --> 01:54:11,821
弹药用完了
Damn it we're out of ammo.

1445
01:54:13,957 --> 01:54:16,126
飞弹来袭，公鸡，发射诱弹
Smoke in the air! Rooster flares!

1446
01:54:18,828 --> 01:54:19,963
好险啊
That was close.

1447
01:54:22,899 --> 01:54:24,401
没有诱弹了
We're out of flares Mav.

1448
01:54:28,805 --> 01:54:30,607
靠，他已经追上来了
Shit he's already on us.

1449
01:54:35,412 --> 01:54:37,080
情况不妙
This is not good.

1450
01:54:45,288 --> 01:54:47,257
-我们又被击中
-不不不
-We took another hit!
-No no no!

1451
01:54:51,995 --> 01:54:54,331
不能再被击中了
We can't take much more of this.

1452
01:54:54,464 --> 01:54:56,132
逃不了，只能弹跳
We can't outrun this guy. We got to eject.

1453
01:54:56,266 --> 01:54:57,567
-什么？
-必须爬升
-What?
-We need altitude.

1454
01:54:57,667 --> 01:54:59,302
我下令就拉下弹跳把手
Pull the ejection handles the second I tell you.

1455
01:54:59,436 --> 01:55:02,005
-等等
-没别的办法
-Mav wait!
-Rooster there's no other way.

1456
01:55:05,008 --> 01:55:06,776
弹跳…弹跳…
Eject eject eject!

1457
01:55:07,577 --> 01:55:09,613
快拉把手，弹跳
Rooster pull the handle! Eject!

1458
01:55:09,746 --> 01:55:11,181
把手拉不动
It's not working.

1459
01:55:22,025 --> 01:55:23,193
独行侠！
Mav!

1460
01:55:25,662 --> 01:55:27,097
对不起
I'm sorry.

1461
01:55:28,465 --> 01:55:30,100
对不起，呆头鹅
I'm sorry Goose.

1462
01:55:42,712 --> 01:55:46,683
午安，两位，这是你们的救星
Good afternoon ladies and gentlemen.
This is your savior speaking.

1463
01:55:46,816 --> 01:55:48,218
请系好安全带
Please fasten your seat belts

1464
01:55:48,351 --> 01:55:51,388
收好桌子，竖直椅背
return your tray tables to their locked and upright positions

1465
01:55:52,355 --> 01:55:54,658
准备降落
and prepare for landing.

1466
01:55:57,060 --> 01:55:59,162
刽子手，你看起来不赖
Hey Hangman you look good.

1467
01:55:59,296 --> 01:56:02,699
我很厉害，公鸡，非常厉害
I am good Rooster. I'm very good.

1468
01:56:04,534 --> 01:56:06,169
航母上见
I'll see you back on deck.

1469
01:56:28,024 --> 01:56:29,559
我顺风飞行
Maverick is downwind.

1470
01:56:29,693 --> 01:56:33,029
没有起落架或尾钩 收起阻拦索，架起护网
No front landing gear. No tailhook.
Pull the cable and raise the barricade.

1471
01:56:33,163 --> 01:56:35,665
紧急迫降，架起护网！
Foul deck! Raise the barricade!

1472
01:56:36,360 --> 01:56:37,740
Go!

1473
01:57:00,257 --> 01:57:02,392
别告诉我引擎失效了
Please don't tell me we lost an engine.

1474
01:57:02,525 --> 01:57:05,061
-好，那我就不说
-好吧
-All right I won't tell you that.
-Okay.

1475
01:57:28,985 --> 01:57:29,920
还好吧？
You good?

1476
01:57:30,587 --> 01:57:32,155
我很好
Yeah. I'm good.

1477
01:58:18,001 --> 01:58:20,437
-你又击落一架敌机
-两架了
-Chalked yourself another kill.
-That makes two.

1478
01:58:21,071 --> 01:58:24,074
独行侠击落五架，他才是王牌
Mav has five. Makes him an ace.

1479
01:58:42,092 --> 01:58:44,327
米契尔上校…
Captain Mitchell! Captain Mitchell!

1480
01:58:51,334 --> 01:58:52,402
长官
Sir.

1481
01:58:59,910 --> 01:59:01,711
谢谢你救我一命
Thank you for saving my life.

1482
01:59:03,013 --> 01:59:05,081
我爸也会这么做
It's what my dad would've done.

1483
01:59:44,120 --> 01:59:45,121
嘿，独行侠
Hey Mav.

1484
01:59:46,256 --> 01:59:47,357
吉米
Jimmy.

1485
01:59:50,527 --> 01:59:51,895
潘妮在吗？
Is... Is Penny around?

1486
01:59:52,028 --> 01:59:55,265
她带艾蜜莉雅去航船
She took Amelia on a sailing trip.

1487
01:59:58,034 --> 01:59:59,035
有说几时回来吗？
Did she say when she'd be back?

1488
02:00:00,170 --> 02:00:01,805
她没说喔
You know she didn't.

1489
02:00:03,974 --> 02:00:05,108
你要喝什么吗？
Can I get you anything?

1490
02:03:06,756 --> 02:03:07,757
（谨献给东尼史考特）

1491
02:10:03,320 --> 02:10:05,322
字幕翻譯：黃文俊
雙語校對：秦仁


